name: Super Fruit TD
description:
Fight off the enemies with super powered fruit! How long can you survive the onslaught?

Controls:
Mouse - Most controls are easily distinguishble
M - Mutes sound.
Q - Strawberry tower buy

W - Watermelon tower buy

E - Banana tower buy

R - Orange tower buy

S - Pineapple tower buy

D - Cherry tower buy

F - Grape tower buy

Version 1.0
Versions 2.0 plans: Apple tower, tower attack abilities, enemy health bars, more enemies, bosses, and possibly a new layout!
